---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - B2Bbaby" description="Professional baby products manufacturer and sourcing expert from China with 15+ years experience.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">About B2Bbaby</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Your trusted partner for certified baby products from China. 15+ years of experience serving brands worldwide.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <article class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                Founded in 2010 with a mission to provide high-quality, safe baby products to the global market, 
                we have grown into a trusted manufacturer and sourcing partner for brands worldwide.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                With <strong>15+ years of experience</strong> in the baby products industry, we understand the importance of 
                safety, quality, and reliability. Every product we produce goes through rigorous quality 
                control and meets international safety standards.
              </p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-6">
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">200+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Staff</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">10,000</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">sqm Factory</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">30+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Countries Served</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="h-80 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=baby%20product%20showroom%20display%2C%20sample%20exhibition%20room%2C%20strollers%20safety%20gates%20high%20chairs%20on%20display%2C%20modern%20showroom&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="B2Bbaby product showroom"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-blue-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Our Core Values</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-lg">Safety First</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Products meet and exceed international safety standards including ASTM, EN, and CPC requirements</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-lg">Quality Commitment</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Rigorous QC at every stage of production - from raw materials to final packaging</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-lg">Partner Success</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Your success is our priority - we work closely with you to ensure market success</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Export Markets Served</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">We proudly serve brands across the globe with proven track record:</p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-blue-800">North America</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  United States
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Canada
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Mexico
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-100">
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-green-800">Western Europe</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Germany
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  United Kingdom
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  France, Netherlands
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-100">
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-purple-800">Oceania</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Australia
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  New Zealand
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-orange-100">
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-3 text-orange-800">Asia-Pacific</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-600 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Japan
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  South Korea
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                  Singapore
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Certifications & Audit Reports</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
              <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100">
                <img 
                  src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=ISO%209001%20certificate%20document%2C%20official%20quality%20management%20system%20certification&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                  alt="ISO 9001 Certificate"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-1">ISO 9001:2015</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Cert #: CN-123456-QMS</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Valid until 2028-05</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
              <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100">
                <img 
                  src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=CE%20certification%20mark%20on%20baby%20product%2C%20EU%20conformity%20certificate&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                  alt="CE Certificate"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-1">CE Marking</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Cert #: BGP-CE-2026-001</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Verified 2026-03</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
              <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100">
                <img 
                  src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=CPC%20certificate%20document%2C%20US%20CPSC%20children%20product%20certificate&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                  alt="CPC Certificate"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-1">CPC</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Cert #: CPC-BGP-ST-2026</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Verified 2026-02</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
              <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100">
                <img 
                  src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=BSCI%20social%20compliance%20certificate%2C%20ethical%20manufacturing%20audit&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                  alt="BSCI Certificate"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-1">BSCI</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Cert #: BSCI-12345678</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Audit score: A</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
              <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100">
                <img 
                  src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=Sedex%20SMETA%20certificate%2C%20ethical%20trade%20audit%20report&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                  alt="Sedex Certificate"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-1">Sedex</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Cert #: SMETA-2026-045</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">2026 Full Audit</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-neutral-200">
              <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-100">
                <img 
                  src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=Disney%20FAMA%20certificate%2C%20manufacturer%20approval%20document&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                  alt="Disney FAMA"
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="p-4">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-1">Disney FAMA</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Cert #: FAMA-BGP-2026</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Available on request</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center mt-6 text-sm text-neutral-500">
            Full certification documents available upon request
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Our Facility</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=baby%20stroller%20assembly%20line%20in%20factory%2C%20workers%20working%2C%20clean%20professional%20workshop&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="Production floor - Baby stroller assembly line"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=quality%20control%20laboratory%20in%20factory%2C%20testing%20equipment%2C%20professional%20setup&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="Quality control laboratory"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=modern%20warehouse%20and%20shipping%20facility%2C%20organized%2C%20boxes%20ready%20to%20ship&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="Warehouse and shipping facility"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Trade Shows & Exhibitions</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=baby%20product%20trade%20show%20booth%2C%20professional%20exhibition%2C%20baby%20strollers%20displayed&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="Trade show booth at baby products exhibition"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=Canton%20Fair%20exhibition%20hall%2C%20large%20trade%20show%2C%20international%20buyers&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="Canton Fair exhibition"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="h-64 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
              <img 
                src="https://trae-api-cn.mchost.guru/api/ide/v1/text_to_image?prompt=professional%20business%20meeting%20at%20trade%20show%2C%20handshake%2C%20business%20discussion&image_size=landscape_4_3"
                alt="Business meeting at trade show"
                class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition duration-300"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center mt-4 text-neutral-500 text-sm">
            We participate in major trade shows including Canton Fair, HK Baby Products Fair, and ABC Kids Expo
          </p>
        </article>

        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition text-lg">
            Partner With Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>